      1          /**
      2           *  @file       SetLoadQueue.c
      3           *
      4           *  @brief      Module where API005 Set Load requests are stored and executed on Application layer
      5           *
      6           *  @details    This module can be used in API005LowLevel module replacing direct Hbl__SetLoadRequest calls
      7           *              It stores all data into a SETLOADQUEUE_MAX_LENGTH bytes buffer when e.g. PC-Control mode is engaged
      8           *              and calls Hbl__SetLoadRequest() to set that request in SetLoadQueue__Handler() that can be called in Application layer.
      9           *              - SETLOADQUEUE_MAX_LENGTH defines maximum size for buffer to store data; for every load it saves 3 bytes + Load data size.
     10           *
     11           *  @section    Applicable_Documents
     12           *					List here all the applicable documents if needed. <tr>	
     13           *
     14           *  $Header: $
     15           *
     16           *  @copyright  Copyright 2018-$Date$. Whirlpool Corporation. All rights reserved - CONFIDENTIAL
     17           */
